    "body": "the return value of window.open is a BrowserWindow so you can just call the loadUrl method to change the content of the window.\n\nI just tested the following code:\n\n``` javascript\nvar noteWindow = window.open('about:blank','noteWindow','');\nnoteWindow.loadUrl(\"http://msn.com\");\n```\n\nhttps://github.com/atom/atom-shell/blob/master/docs/api/browser-window.md\n\nhttps://github.com/atom/atom-shell/blob/master/docs/api/browser-window.md#browserwindowloadurlurl\n"
